
Before Devops.
  The development team develops and tests the code, and the operation team deploies/releases the code into production. And 
  there is a time gap and misunderstandings between the dev team operation team. We need to minimise the time gap and increase the effecicence of the releases.
  Devops helps to meet the required criteria.

What is Devops?

Devops is the combination of culture philoosophies, practices and tools that increases an organization's ability to deliver application and service at heigh velocity.
Devops is combination of Dev team and Operation team.

What is the work of Devops engineer?

Devops is all about automation of processes. Devops engineer should automate the manual tasks which doesn't requrie manual involvement.
This is achived by using diffrent tools. 
